verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Jesus!  The Name that charms our fears,
That bids our sorrows cease;
‘Tis music in the sinner’s ears;
‘Tis life, and health, and peace.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}He breaks the power of canceled sin;
He sets the prisoner free.
His blood can make the foulest clean;
His Life availed for me.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Hear Him, ye deaf, His praise ye dumb
Your loosened tongues employ;
Ye blind, behold your Savior come,
And leap ye lame for joy.{/lang-eng}
